# Copy to secrets.tpl and add entries like:
#
#     KEY="op://ExampleVault/exampleFolder/EXAMPLE_SECRET_REFERENCE"
#
# `./install mac` runs `op inject` to resolve these into `secrets`, linked to
# ~/.secrets.local and sourced by zshenv. secrets.tpl is gitignored: op:// refs
# aren't secrets, but they name your vaults and items.
